# ChatOps - Generic Cisco Spark Bot
## A basic starting place with logging and working examples.
---

1. Install Node.js v8 or higher - https://nodejs.org

2. Get a SPARK_TOKEN for your Cisco Spark bot - https://developer.ciscospark.com/add-bot.html

3. Clone down this repository to your computer:

`git clone https://github.com/ernestgwilsonii/genericCiscoSparkBot.git`

4. Install the required modules:

`npm install`

5. Set environment variable:

#Windows:

`set SPARK_TOKEN=PutYourBotsTokenHere`

#Linux:

`export SPARK_TOKEN=PutYourBotsTokenHere`

6. Start the bot:

`npm start`

---
